    "11167696": {
      "title": "Optimum spinsqueezing in Bose-Einstein condensates with particle losses",
      "abstract": "The problem of spin squeezing with a bimodal condensate in the presence of particle losses is solved analytically by the Monte Carlo wave function method. We find the largest obtainable spin squeezing as a function of the one-body loss rate, the two-body and three-body rate constants, and the s-wave scattering length."
